	<div style="text-align:right;">
		FUGAçA, Cyllian Arias<sup>1</sup>; SANTOS NETO, Rene Scalet Dos<sup>2</sup>; SILVA, Margarete Mara da<sup>3</sup>; KUSMA, Solena Ziemer<sup>4</sup>; BISCAIA, Evellyn Silverio<sup>5</sup>; RIELLA, Miguel Carlos<sup>6</sup>		<BR>
